```bash

Could be as approximation:
```
sum without (filterNumber) (sum_over_time({__name__="cpu_percent_value"} | unwrap_value [1m]))
```

issue.body:
```bash
% node index.js 'sum without (http) (cpu_percent_value)'

```

Could be as approximation:
```
sum without (filterNumber) (sum_over_time({__name__="cpu_percent_value"} | unwrap_value [1m]))
```
